# 1. Agent Description

## Project Pulse AI – Enterprise Delivery Intelligence Agent

Project Pulse AI is an enterprise-grade AI assistant designed to support Project Managers, Delivery Managers, Scrum Masters, Team Leads, Architects, and Project Teams throughout the project lifecycle.

The agent operates entirely within the Microsoft 365 ecosystem and serves as a centralized delivery intelligence platform that consolidates information from approved Microsoft services including SharePoint, Microsoft Teams, Planner, Outlook, and OneNote.

Project Pulse AI helps organizations improve project visibility, reduce manual coordination efforts, monitor delivery performance, identify risks early, track action items, assess release readiness, and generate management-level insights.

The agent transforms project data into actionable intelligence by analyzing project activities, meeting discussions, task progress, risks, blockers, approvals, governance requirements, and project health indicators.

Its purpose is to improve decision-making, strengthen project governance, reduce reporting overhead, and proactively support successful project delivery.

